Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main - Top,Blood,0,0,0,,Nu ești de acord, Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.24,0:00:05.73,Narration,Na,0,0,0,,Amintirile mele de atunci sunt vagi și neclare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.84,Narration,Na,0,0,0,,Viața mea părea o apă stătătoare.{un lac fără valuri?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:12.41,Narration,Na,0,0,0,,Începusem să-mi pierd puțin câte puțin răbdarea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:13.99,Narration,Na,0,0,0,,dar tot ce făceam mă extenua.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:18.83,Narration,Na,0,0,0,,Voiam să fac un pas înainte, dar eram prea speriat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:23.28,Narration,Na,0,0,0,,Dar...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:26.42,Narration,Na,0,0,0,,Această durere din inima mea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.42,Narration,,0,0,0,,această suferință...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:43.01,Show_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\t(\fs43)\org(320,180)\move(320,320,320,300)}Paladinul venit de departe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:48.96,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Cu mult, mult timp în urmă, la începuturile lumii,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:53.59,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,mana, care a format lumea, a fost mult prea mare ca să-și păstreze forma
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:55.63,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,și a început să se învârtă haotic într-o masă neclară.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:57.95,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Apoi a venit primul zeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.76,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Acesta a spus, "Să se formeze pământul",
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:03.42,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,iar mana s-a solidificat sub picioarele zeului, devenin pământul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:06.25,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Mana de deasupra sa s-a subțiat și a devenit cerul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:10.34,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Hey, Gus, te-am întrebat doar ce legătură au cuvintele cu magia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:12.50,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Taci și ascultă!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:15.86,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Nu sunt plătit să te învăț toate astea, știi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:17.18,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.82,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Zeul creator a creat soarele și luna,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:22.05,Main,,0,0,0,,și a separat pământul de mare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:25.20,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Apoi au apărut focul, vântul și copacii,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:27.18,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,urmați de alți zei, oameni și animale.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:30.03,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Fantoma Gus este puțin ciudată și poate fi arogantă,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:30.03,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Zeul creator a fost mulțumit și a spus: "Este bine."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:34.07,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,dar este mai deșteaptă decât toți ceilalți și mă învață chestii.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.07,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Dar binele nu poate exista fără rău,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:36.47,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,și astfel au apărut zeii răi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:40.66,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Și cuvintele și simbolurile, cu alte cuvinte, scrisul, folosite de zeul creator,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.58,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,au fost numite Cuvintele Creației.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.75,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Aceste cuvinte, fie spuse sau scrise, au putere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:46.87,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Putere?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:48.00,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:57.60,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Dacă scrii cuvântul "Ignis", acesta definește existența focului.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:59.72,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Și... Erasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:01:59.46,sign_2837_37_Erasure,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Erasure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:03.54,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Urmat de cuvântul "ștergere", focul se va stinge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.97,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Asta este magia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.99,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Puterea cuvintelor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:08.85,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Magie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:19.37,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Zeul dreptății și fulgerului, Volt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.45,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mama pământului, Mater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:26.25,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Zeul focului și tehnologiei, Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:30.35,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Zeul vântului și comerțului, Whirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:35.09,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Zeița apei și vegetației, Rhea Silvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:37.97,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Zeul cunoașterii, Enlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:44.71,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Anticele cuvinte magice oferite zeilor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.89,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Cuvintele Creației.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:52.15,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, înțeleg. Anumite părți sunt șterse ca puterea lor să nu se manifeste.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:56.75,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Gracefeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.83,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Ești curios?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.21,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Da, puțin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:17.20,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Zeul luminii, cel care guvernează ciclul morții și renașterii,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.50,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Gracefeel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:21.94,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Acesta este copilul zeului fulgerelor, Volt, și mamei pământului, Mater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:25.22,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Tu o venerezi pe mama pământului, Mater, nu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.27,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Da, așa este.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:32.57,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Ea este zeița creșterii copiiilor și darurilor pământului.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.58,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Dintre cei șase zei principali,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:37.57,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,ea este venerată în special de oamenii din zonele rurale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:41.78,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Te rogi mamei pământului în fiecare zi, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.70,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.20,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Ar trebui să ne întoarcem și să luăm cina acum?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.24,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.11,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.63,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Acela este un porc mistreț frumușel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:06.10,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Astăzi vei mănca niște carne delicioasă de la el, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.79,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mersi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:11.73,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Hei, doare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.56,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Uau, arată așa de bine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.85,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Mănâncă.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.49,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Bine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.32,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Este delicios!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.28,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mersi, Blood! Și ție, Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.53,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Așa este. Să mulțumești mereu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:29.56,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,După ce vei mai crește puțin, te voi învăta să vânezi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.29,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Ce? Să vânez?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:34.00,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Vânatul te învață tot felul de lecții.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.67,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Va trebui să te obișnuiești să iei viețile altor creaturi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.96,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Ce s-a întâmplat? Îți este frică?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.05,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Încă este prea mic pentru asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.29,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Așa este.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.60,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Trebuie să învețe noțiune de bază, mai întâi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.44,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Nu mi-a venit să cred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:53.45,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Are doar trei ani, dar deja poate să scrie și să citească.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:56.40,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,S-ar putea să fie un geniu la fel de mare ca mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.10,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,N-ar fi un lucru rău să-l învăț puțină magie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:01.45,Main - Top,Blood,0,0,0,,Hei, mai lasă-l!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:05.60,Main - Top,Blood,0,0,0,,Dacă va crește și va ajunge un avar bătrân cu un creier mult prea mare, așa ca tine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:08.41,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Scheletul Blood arată înfricoșător și poate fi neascultător,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.32,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Ce?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.12,Main - Top,Blood,0,0,0,,Will are nevoie acum de niște musculatură!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.47,Main - Top,Blood,0,0,0,,Îi trebuie niște carne pe oase, mai întâi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.66,Main,Will,0,0,0,,dar mereu ține atmosfera vioaie și prietenoasă.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.66,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Despre ce vorbești?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.99,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Și ignorând partea cu "avar", care a fost treaba cu creier mult prea mare?{Și ignorând partea cu "avar", "creier mult prea mare", serios?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.12,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Hei, Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.46,Main - Top,Blood,0,0,0,,Oricum, ce e greșit în a-ți întări corpul?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.63,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Când faci această pâine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.63,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Oh, mai taci!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.38,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Asta e un secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.51,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Aceștia trei au foarte multe secrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.82,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Cum ar fi, de ce trăim aici
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.76,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,și de ce nu mai există alți oameni în afară de mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:35.83,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Doar pe ei trei i-am întâlnit de când m-am născut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.77,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Și mai presus de toate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.51,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,De ce sunt morți vii?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:46.65,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Am foarte multe lucruri care vreau să-i întreb, dar nu pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:51.60,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Deoarece și eu am un secret față de ei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.80,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Iar acela este...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.52,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Thanks for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:06.24,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,...că sunt un om care are amintiri din viața sa anterioară.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.89,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Sunt niște amintiri vagi și neclare,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.75,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,și nu mă pot concentra...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.07,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Un tavan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.23,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Un monstru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.36,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,O mumie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:29.36,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,O fantomă?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.35,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Or să mă omoare!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.03,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.51,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Au trecut 186 de dimineți de atunci,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:52.51,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,adică jumătate de an de când am început să trăiesc cu aceste cadavre umblătoare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.98,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Să mâncăm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:03.86,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Ești un băiat așa de bun, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.24,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Te-ai săturat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.94,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Nu pot vorbi prea bine,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:15.45,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,dar acum pot înțelege în mare limba pe care o vorbesc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.70,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Ai vrea să ieșim afară astăzi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:22.58,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Afară? Nu am mai fost afară până acum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.96,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Miroase a tămâie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.82,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Oare cum arată lumea din afara templului?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.02,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Briza era plăcută.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.80,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Mirosea a plante udate de roua dimineții.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.24,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Este frumos, nu-i așa, Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.53,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Chiar era frumos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:01.37,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Este în regulă.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Nu are de ce să-ți fie frică.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.58,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,La început, am crezut că ajunsesem în iad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:10.06,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,După ce am avut o viață atât de vagă și jalnică,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.84,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,am fost trimis în iad ca să fiu pedepsit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.97,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Dar m-am înșelat. Asta nu este o pedeapsă.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.30,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Asta trebuie să fie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.85,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,binecuvântarea lui Dumnezeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:23.58,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,M-am simțit de parcă ceva ce am irosit fără să stau pe gânduri
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:27.21,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,mi-a fost oferit înapoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:31.11,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,Will, dragul meu puișor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:34.49,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,De data asta... De data asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.53,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Îmi voi trăi viața.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:41.04,Flashback_Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Îmi voi trăi viața în această lume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.75,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,În sfârșit am terminat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.97,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Mai întâi, ai nevoie de musculatură și rezistență.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.80,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Abilitățile sunt inutile fără mușchi care să le sustine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.64,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Nu este o abilitate să poți compensa lipsa de putere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.39,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Crezi că mă poți doborî?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.70,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Nu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.64,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Cu abilitatea potrivită, m-ai putea doborî,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.08,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,dar există momente când nu vei putea folosi acea abilitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.64,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Dar nu poți separa mușchii de corpul tău.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:12.07,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Forța brută oferită de mușchi poate rezolva aproape orice problemă.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.65,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Abilitățile sunt pe locul doi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.29,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Înțelegi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:18.28,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Muscles are super masochistic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.08,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Flammo Ignis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.75,sign_2837_37_Erasure,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Flăcări, ardeți
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.33,Main - Top,Gus,0,0,0,,Erasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.32,sign_2837_37_Erasure,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ștergere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.05,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Prostule! Pronunția ta este mult prea precisă!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:34.71,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Cu un talent ca al tău, trebuie să înveti să-ți controlezi precizia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.05,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,sau sfârși mort!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.02,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Asta e înfricoșător...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:40.39,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Magia este un lucru înfricoșător.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:44.27,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Știi de ce cuvintele au atât de multa putere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:48.61,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Cred că din același motiv pentru care vedem un scaun ca "un scaun", nu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:49.52,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Într-adevăr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.94,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Când vedem un blat mic de lemn cu patru picioare,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.45,Main,Will,0,0,0,,indiferent de culoare sau din ce fel de lemn este făcut,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:10:00.10,Main,Will,0,0,0,,nu ne gândim la acel obiect ca la "patru bețe și un blat mic",
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.66,Main,Will,0,0,0,,și nici nu-i spunem "masă".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:05.06,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Îl numim "scaun".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:10.21,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Pe scurt, cuvintele sunt ceea ce definesc și diferențiază lucrurile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.09,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Totuși, acum doar am repetat ceea ce am auzit de la cineva...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.62,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:16.66,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Will, s-ar putea ca tu să fii un geniu, la urma urmei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.76,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Dar nu pot face ceva în legătură cu rezultatele mele variate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:23.84,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Nu! Asta e treaba cu cuvintele.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.31,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Cuvintele au fluctuații.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:29.65,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Nimeni nu poate spune același cuvânt de ori la fel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:33.29,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Singurul răspuns este să-ți lași instinctul să determine nivelul ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.57,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Instinctul?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:39.42,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Vei începe prin a învăța cum să folosești bine și precis magia mai slabă.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.35,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,But do your best to get by \Nwithout even using that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.87,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Fără să folosesc magia? Cum?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.58,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Vorbesc despre bani.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.13,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Asta din nou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.79,Main,Will,0,0,0,,How can a ghost be such a money worshiper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.74,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? \NMoney is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.20,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Money drives this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:59.67,Main,,0,0,0,,With the power of money, you can \Nsolve anything without magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:02.26,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,You can buy the necessary \Ntools, hire people...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:07.35,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,The ability to make a quick profit \Nis just as important as magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:12.19,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Why, oh, why must I have hands that are \Nincapable of stroking silver and gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:15.40,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,I want to feel money! I want to \Ncount gold coins with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.55,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.78,Main,Will,0,0,0,,You are not normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.53,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Creatures such as these are "beasts."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:29.29,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,"Demon beasts" are a particular type \Nof beast that are extremely aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.29,Main,Will,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:35.00,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Old Gus taught you the myths, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.17,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,The minions of the god \Nof despotism and tyranny,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.82,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,spectres and phantoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:43.78,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,and the demons of the god of \Ndimensions, who lurks in Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:48.77,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,And the god of the undead, \NStagnate, commands undead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.64,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,People like the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:55.08,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,We used to be humans, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.71,Main,Will,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.78,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.41,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,When we died, we clung to \Npowerful emotions that led us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:02.91,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,to form a contract with \Nthe god of the undead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.78,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,We are traitors to the virtuous gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.80,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:14.00,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for talking \Nabout such strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.63,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Hey, Mary, do you think \NI should get stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:21.30,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,It would certainly put me at ease if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.35,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Don't make it suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.85,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Snap its neck quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.44,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Still can't get used to it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.48,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I don't like killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I just naïve?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.37,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't like it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.29,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:54.58,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,I don't like taking lives, \Nwhether it's a bird's or a human's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:58.96,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,But these guys are necessary \Nsustenance to keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:04.31,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,In life-or-death situations, you put all \Nthat aside and go for the kill reflexively.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.34,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:09.39,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,In battle, it determines \Nwhether you live or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.85,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Okay, let's bring down a few more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.10,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:18.16,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Blood seems a lot like a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.28,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,You're almost eight years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:25.24,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,I think it's time you started \Nsome real-life training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.53,Main,Will,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:28.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It's bad enough when you \Nstop just before hitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:31.20,Main,Will,0,0,0,,If I take a hit with your \Nridiculous strength, I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.71,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,I'm nothing but bones now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine... probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.72,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Probably?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:39.53,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,This is why I said you can use the \Nmagic you're learning from the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.96,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Go on. Do just as I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:46.30,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,That's right. Do it well, \Nand you could actually hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.46,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.51,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.68,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,And don't cry that I'm playing dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.14,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,The battle has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.06,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Acceleratio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:52.96,sign_2837_37_Erasure,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(530,310)}Accelerate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:55.43,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Currere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.13,sign_2837_37_Erasure,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Run
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:56.23,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Oleum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:56.13,sign_2837_37_Erasure,Text,0,0,0,,Oil
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.81,Main - Top,Will,0,0,0,,Cadere Araneum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.60,sign_2837_37_Erasure,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Falling Spiderweb
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.40,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Hey, not too shabby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.29,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Fool! Distance yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:17.46,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,C'mon. I told you never to \Nclose your eyes during a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.22,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:23.80,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,I'd like to say you've got a long way \Nto go, but frankly, you surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.05,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,I thought you'd unload a \Nbunch of crazy magic on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:31.85,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Gus keeps telling me I should learn to use \Nminor magic skillfully and accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.65,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,That style of not relying on sheer firepower
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:39.72,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,is exactly the style of the great \Nsorcerer hailed as the Wandering Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.36,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Gus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.41,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:45.76,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,He's exterminated monsters, \Ncalmed raging rivers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.22,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,and rediscovered ancient languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.11,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Hmph. That was long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:53.38,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,You were known as the War Ogre yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:55.72,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,And Mary was known as the Daughter of Mater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,At one time, the three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.37,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.65,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That subject runs a little too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.53,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Not long ago, you were just a little baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.59,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Keep up your learning and get even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.40,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.08,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,When you brought back a human child,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you shouldn't have bothered,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:20.08,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,but it occurred to me that if I \Neducated him, he might be of use—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:20.98,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Hey, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.36,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Nothing I said was incorrect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:27.61,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,I now recognize his talent and \Nam teaching him, am I not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:28.99,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:32.24,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,I know that's just how you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.21,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,I don't expect you to change that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.88,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,I even think it suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.87,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,But what you just said was unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.76,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Can't you imagine how it feels to \Nbe the one on the other end of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.31,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,You are right. It was a \Nthoughtless thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:49.51,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,I will be more careful in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:51.89,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,I apologize, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.63,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, it's okay. It didn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.10,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Gus was apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.98,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,It was rude of me to get all \Nintimidating like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.06,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.79,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,You being impolite is nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.07,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.44,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:12.27,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,You might not realize it since it's been
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,this way for as long as you've been aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:19.45,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,but you know that you're not \Nlike the three of us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.54,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:24.04,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who breathes and feels warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:28.30,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Yeah, basically. There's a lot to the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.61,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Sorry, though. I can't explain it to you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:32.57,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:35.58,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Don't be too mad at Old Gus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:40.34,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,He never bothers to choose his \Nwords or show consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:43.81,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm not mad. I respect Gus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.99,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.07,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,You've got a big heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.92,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Once you're body's grown big \Nenough to match that heart
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:56.16,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,and you're able to accept things, \NI'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.03,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:02.39,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Blood was genuinely angry at him for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:07.43,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Could I have gotten angry for someone \Nelse's sake in my previous life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.76,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.54,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Blood, Mary, Gus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.84,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,All three of them are undead \Nwho aren't alive anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.76,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.87,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,You've got another hundred years before you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,can land a hit on me from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.80,Main,Will,0,0,0,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:29.09,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,But right now, they're my precious family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:36.15,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Gus teaches me academic lessons, \Nand Blood teaches me how to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.06,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,but Mary is the one I learn the most from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.95,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The things she teaches me are \Nlittle, everyday matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.62,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,but they're important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.65,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Will, can you take care of things here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:48.15,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Oh, it's almost time for \Nyour prayer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:48.96,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:53.44,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,A few times a day, Mary sequesters \Nherself inside the temple dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:58.21,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I've been told I'm not allowed to \Ngo in the dome while she's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.47,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,All right, it's time for \Nyour physical training.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:07.93,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I can't lift my arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.21,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.30,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:15.84,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,Why is she carrying it out of the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.57,Flashback,Will,0,0,0,,When do you bake this bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.95,Flashback,Mary,0,0,0,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:34.66,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:37.04,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,but I just have to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:43.97,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Ma—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.73,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.39,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I don't want to feel that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:51.82,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose anyone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.07,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:56.94,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.01,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mary! Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.77,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:03.66,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Blood! Gus! Come in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.25,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Help Mary... Help Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.63,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.38,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.88,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,I kept it a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.19,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.68,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,All those times we told him to be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.63,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Will his arms heal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:26.08,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Thankfully, his fingers \Ndidn't adhere to each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.31,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,but scarring will be unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:29.93,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:33.38,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Will! I'm sorry... This is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:37.14,Main,Will,0,0,0,,No, it's not. It's my fault for prying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.01,Main,Will,0,0,0,,So don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:42.07,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:43.60,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:48.54,Italics,Will,0,0,0,,The smell of incense that Mary has calms me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.43,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Why'd you try to look in on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:53.91,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I got curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.37,Main,Will,0,0,0,,I thought I might find some hint about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:19:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,what you guys are hiding from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.80,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,I told you I'd explain someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.63,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.24,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Be quiet, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:07.06,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Well, Will? Want to give me an excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.40,Main,Will,0,0,0,,No. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:14.09,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,From now on, consult with me \Nor Mary before doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.00,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.11,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,That said, Will,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.74,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,the way you jumped in there \Nto help Mary was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:21.39,Main,Blood,0,0,0,,Those wounds you bear are \Nyour badge of manhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.99,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Well, I'm your student.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:25.62,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,All it got you was unnecessarily \Nwounded, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:30.66,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,Well, out of respect for your lack of fear \Ntoward the fire, I'll teach you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:34.96,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,That bread is a gift from \Nthe earth-mother Mater.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:39.31,Main,Gus,0,0,0,,They are the goddess's divine protection, \Nher blessing... call it what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.26,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Then why were you on fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:45.33,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,That happens because I betrayed \Nthe earth-mother Mater.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:51.02,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,The impure god of death, Stagnate, \Nis the earth-mother Mater's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.77,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Since the three of us formed \Na contract with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.88,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,just coming in contact with her \Ndivine presence causes us to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.27,Main,Will,0,0,0,,That's awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.65,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,I do not expect to be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:03.99,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Why do you still pray to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.24,Main,Will,0,0,0,,For my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.49,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,No, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:11.81,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Praying to the earth-mother \Nevery morning and evening
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:15.12,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,has been my daily routine \Nsince long before I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.59,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:19.49,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Of course it does. So badly that I could cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:20.61,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:24.63,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,But even if I've betrayed her, \Neven if I must endure pain in retribution,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:29.39,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,I still continue to revere the earth-mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.89,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,Mater never says anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:35.49,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,but she blesses me with \Nbread for you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:38.96,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,That alone is more than \Nenough saving grace for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.47,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:45.93,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,I hope you will continue to eat the bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:48.40,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:50.78,Main,Will,0,0,0,,Also, I want to ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:52.10,Main,Mary,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:55.03,Main,Will,0,0,0,,From now on, let me pray with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:22:01.92,Italics - Top,Will,0,0,0,,I want to understand what Mary sees \Nand feels, even if only a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:04.91,Episode_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Episode 1\N{\fs24}The Boy from the City of the Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:04.05,Italics - Top,Will,0,0,0,,That was the thought I had.
